-- Simple English Advice - Gestor/Consultancy services based in Malaga
('Simple English Advice', 'Gestor', 'English-speaking gestor and expat consultancy dedicated to helping foreigners live, work, and settle in Spain without the endless paperwork headaches. Founded by Delroy & Christina, British expats with 25 years of living in Malaga and 15 years of helping people navigate Spanish bureaucracy. Services include: vehicle ownership transfers (€60 + taxes), UK to Spanish driving licence exchange, EU vehicle registration/matriculation (from €625), NRA/NRUA rental registration number (mandatory for Airbnb/Booking.com from July 2025), annual NRA renewal compliance reports, DGT vehicle reports and documentation, vehicle de-registrations (bajas), ITV services, property management agreements, mortgage fee refunds, digital nomad visa assistance, autonomo registration, non-resident tax filings, NIE/TIE applications, and general Spanish bureaucratic support. Also offers website design, SEO and GEO services with 15+ years experience helping businesses reach English-speaking audiences. Based in Andalucía with network of trusted contacts across Spain. Transparent fixed pricing with no hidden fees. Many services handled completely online via email or WhatsApp without office visits. Bilingual team providing practical, straightforward advice in simple English with no jargon.', 'Remote/Online service (based in Malaga)', 'Malaga', 'Málaga', '+34 951 74 51 68', 'info@simpleenglishadvice.com', 'https://simpleenglishadvice.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
